      for the other selectors.We use the list (rectangular)list("rectangular")
        rather than the symbol rectangularstring "rectangular" to allow for the possibility
        of operations with multiple arguments, not all of the same
        type.  The interface also defines
      the constructors to be used by the external system.The
        type the constructors are installed under neednt be a list because
        a constructor is always used to make an object of one particular
        type.
      These are
      identical to Bens internally defined constructors, except that they
      attach the tag.

