Implement the constructor make-from-mag-angmake_from_mag_ang in message-passing style. This procedurefunction should be analogous to the make-from-real-imagmake_from_real_imag procedurefunction given above.
make_from_mag_ang_message_passing square_definition apply_generic_message_passing generic_selectors_message_passing Error message_passing_example
function make_from_mag_ang(r, a) { function dispatch(op) { return op === "real_part" ? r * math_cos(a) : op === "imag_part" ? r * math_sin(a) : op === "magnitude" ? r : op === "angle" ? a : Error("Unknown op in make_from_real_imag", op); } return dispatch; }
